sub_title: Managing Partner at DSBP Consultants  | Rotterdamse Zakenvrouw 2019
summary: Nan Su funded Dutch Sino Business Promotions (DSBP) in 2006. DSBP specializes in supporting Dutch and Chinese businesses looking to explore each other's markets, focusing on three core sectors; (regional) Government-to-Government, Agriculture & Horticulture, and GreenTech solutions.
